{"tid":1246342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李明逵: 我會抗命，我會留下來直至最後一分鐘","createTime":"2019-06-20T16:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T02:16:20.000Z","uid":49753,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ee0b2ccb80d10daab2a7cafcde81d77a78523f3","tid":1246342,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"在中國全權之下的香港，<br />\n我們可能要違背自己的意願，<br />\n執行我們不想執行的任務。<br />\n被逼幹不道德或錯誤的事，<br />\n我會抗命。<br />\n我會留下來直至最後一分鐘，<br />\n因為這是我的家，<br />\n我生於斯長於斯，<br />\n是香港把我教育成材的，<br />\n我要留下來服務港人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88iZNDN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88iZNDN.png&h=fd26bef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/theoldhongkong/videos/2862741033751825/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftheoldhongkong%2Fvideos%2F2862741033751825%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=15f071cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/theoldhongkong/videos/2862741033751825/</a>"},{"pid":"df69584f8bca2b536179e664d05bd7734e78d451","tid":1246342,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"結果成件事好似冇前一哥出過聲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8b3d47b830402b3b6ff94c5bc8ee9399bd0e26","tid":1246342,"uid":98726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b09c3b1ead0e392fffd57ead2c0a196a6bbaa918","tid":1246342,"uid":47905,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"以前就係<br />\n依家個D 依家當打人 屈人為樂<br />\n平時就HEA到收工"},{"pid":"2fca8e989dada90dbcbd4ed74aec53bc362b96a4","tid":1246342,"uid":149494,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"三十年前個個藝人都話要爭取民主自由"},{"pid":"f86ebeb95ecb2fb03405901efd982c03115694c8","tid":1246342,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score